room_title: Escape room "Zombie Escape" by Escape Room Fayetteville in Fayetteville
review: I went to the escape room on Saturday and it was an amazing experience! We did the zombie escape with Mikey and he was great. I would definitely come back when Mikey is working again.

room_title: Escape room "Zombie Escape" by Escape Room Fayetteville in Fayetteville
review: Fun and challenging. We did the Zombie room. It was an exciting hour. Carson and the other staff were friendly, attentive, and helpful. We will be back.
